; UNSAT: (x * x + y * y + 1) == 0 for 10-bit x, y
; Domain: 1024^2 = 1M — was above old compiled threshold (65536)
; No solution: sum of squares + 1 is always >= 1
; Expected: UNSAT
1 sort bitvec 10
2 sort bitvec 1
3 input 1 x
4 input 1 y
5 mul 1 3 3
6 mul 1 4 4
7 add 1 5 6
8 one 1
9 add 1 7 8
10 zero 1
11 eq 2 9 10
12 bad 11
